description:
As an Admin
    I should be able to Create, Read, Update, and Delete a Capability.
name: Capability

elements.name: Create a Capability

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
The user is on the Capabilities page
The user creates a Capability
The user should be redirected to the details page of the created Capability
The user should see the created details of the Capability

elements.name: Read Capability details from the list

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user navigates to the Capabilities page
The user should see the details of the Capabilities in the table

elements.name: Read Capability details from its page

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user navigates to the ACTIVE Capabilities page
The user should see the details of the ACTIVE Capability

elements.name: Edit a Capability from the list

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user is on the Capabilities page
The user edits a Capability
The user should see the details of the edited Capabilities in the table

elements.name: Edit a Capability from its page

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user navigates to the ACTIVE Capabilities page
The user edits the Capability
The user should see the edited details of the Capability

elements.name: Delete a Capability from its page

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user navigates to the ACTIVE Capabilities page
The user deletes the Capability
The user should be not be able to execute further actions on the Capability

elements.name: Delete a Capability

steps.name: The user is logged in as an Admin
An ACTIVE Capability exists
The user is on the Capabilities page
The user deletes a Capability
The user should not see the details of the deleted Capabilities in the table
